and give it a shot myself!

26:10.109 --> 26:12.609
Great!
We can be a team!

26:12.611 --> 26:15.079
Yeah, right. A team.

26:15.081 --> 26:16.480
Wait, was that sarcasm?

26:16.482 --> 26:18.115
No!

26:18.116 --> 26:19.749
Yeah! Right there!
I'm pretty sure
that's my voice

26:19.752 --> 26:21.518
when I'm being sarcastic.

26:21.520 --> 26:22.086
Okay, Buford,
where are
Phineas and Ferb?

26:22.088 --> 26:24.221
