talking about, Stacy!

27:21.747 --> 27:23.180
Come on!
STACY: Where are you
going?

27:23.182 --> 27:27.151
To my back yard!
The heart of the
mysterious force!

27:27.153 --> 27:29.553
Would you like to
trade two Sartre
for a Nietzsche?

27:29.555 --> 27:30.921
All right.

27:30.923 --> 27:32.089
Sucker!

27:37.096 --> 27:39.696
