33:11.897 --> 33:13.230
Who is Isabella?

33:13.232 --> 33:15.298
The girl who lives
across the street.

33:15.300 --> 33:17.434
Mom says that
talking to neighbors
can be dangerous.

33:17.436 --> 33:19.336
MOM 2D: It's true!
Well, it's time you met
her.

33:19.338 --> 33:20.670
Come on,
you'll like her.

33:20.672 --> 33:22.506
What about
the Normbots?

33:22.508 --> 33:25.509
Relax! We've been
avoiding them all day.

33:25.511 --> 33:28.111
If you're really careful,
you can...

33:28.113 --> 33:29.679
Okay, we've got to be
