Thank you.

37:08.667 --> 37:11.668
Oh, great and powerful
mysterious force!

37:11.670 --> 37:14.371
I know you are
just trying to
protect my brothers

37:14.373 --> 37:16.873
but I am simply trying
to protect them, too,

37:16.875 --> 37:18.675
from their
dangerous inventions.

37:18.677 --> 37:21.444
Show yourself so that
I may reason with you!

37:23.649 --> 37:26.182
Maybe we should
build a shrine to it?

37:26.184 --> 37:27.183
Candace, that's...
(BOTH GASP)

37:27.185 --> 37:28.318
(BOTH SCREAM)

37:28.320 --> 37:30.620
BOTH:
It's a mysterious force!

37:32.524 --> 37:35.325
Ferb! I think we got it!
It looks like home!

37:35.327 --> 37:37.560
What do we do now?

37:37.562 --> 37:39.896
I don't know.
I can't believe
it actually worked.

37:39.898 --> 37:42.565
Well, thanks, everyone.
Hey, where's...

